    <item>
      <title>日本十年期债券拍卖需求创数十年来新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-10-year-bond-auction-shows-weakest-demand-since-2003</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本十年期主权债券拍卖的投资者需求从某种程度上来看是2003年以来最弱的，这再次表明在央行上个月提高利率后，日本金融市场陷入了动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/japan-10-year-bond-auction-shows-weakest-demand-since-2003</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:59:23 GMT</pubDate>
