      <title>美国股指期货在连续三天全球抛售后反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-stock-futures-bounce-back-after-three-day-global-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股指期货上涨，因为在全球股市因担心全球最大经济体可能放缓以及科技股估值过高而经历三天抛售之后，逢低买家纷纷涌现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/us-stock-futures-bounce-back-after-three-day-global-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 00:59:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
